<h2 class="bold font-l">Hokuto Ujou Hagan Ken (EP 43)</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Toki, the messianic archetype of the show, uses the Juu no Ken (Fist of Gentleness) technique known as the Hokuto Ujou Hagan Ken (The Humane Face Breaking Fist of the North Star), which causes the victim to feel intense pleasure before they die. </p>
